div.p:
—John Connally’s good report on his
                        talks with President Medici
                    and Minister Delfim Neto in Brazil;

—we are working overtime to control inflation; sharp increases in coffee prices
                    has produced strong pressure from consumers and wholesalers
                        for action to reverse this trend;

—you are convinced that the best interests of producers and
                        consumers are served by continued international
                        cooperation between the two;
